                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-13-off71 t18080217-13-cd72"></join>, six pound weight of lead, value 18 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18080217-13-victim154" type="victimName">
                           Jonathan 
                           Turner
                        <interp inst="t18080217-13-victim154" type="surname" value="Turner"></interp>
