                     </persName>
                     
                  , affixed to his dwelling house, did rip and cut, with intent feloniously to steal the same
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18080217-13-person155">
                  JONATHAN 
                  TURNER
               <interp inst="t18080217-13-person155" type="surname" value="TURNER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080217-13-person155" type="given" value="JONATHAN"></interp>
